			<td colspan="6" class="DetailTitle" style="text-align:center;">
                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The network will provide a forum for the exchange of ideas in the areas of Networking, Broadcasting and Telecommunications, and their convergence. The network will consist of a select group of academics and industrialist from all three areas, mainly from the UK but also from abroad, with a strong link to a similar European Network (E-NET), who will contribute to the development of an agenda for convergence and facilitate the development of a resarch base in the related fields. The Network will form the steering group to the future PGNets, a set of yearly conferences for the training of young researchers in the UK, which has taken place every year since 2000.</span>
                        </td>
		</tr>
